00:19:48.179 --> 00:19:49.777
The dreamer, yeah. Yeah.

312
00:19:49.779 --> 00:19:51.817
(SIGHS DEEPLY)

313
00:19:54.684 --> 00:19:57.119
And you were able
to just go on?


314
00:19:57.121 --> 00:20:01.623
Courage is the solution
to despair.


315
00:20:01.625 --> 00:20:05.663
Reason provides no answers.

316
00:20:07.298 --> 00:20:09.597
I can't know
what the future will bring.


317
00:20:09.599 --> 00:20:12.703
We have to choose
despite uncertainty.


318
00:20:13.304 --> 00:20:17.972
Wisdom is holding
two contradictory truths


