00:21:22.073 --> 00:21:23.174
Belief...

334
00:21:24.141 --> 00:21:25.810
Forgiveness...

335
00:21:27.644 --> 00:21:30.615
Grace covers us all.

336
00:21:32.849 --> 00:21:34.218
I believe that.

